{"tid":1502372,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"TVB女記者一度被警員包圍查證","createTime":"2019-08-24T15:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T10:40:26.000Z","uid":68738,"like":360,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"ea4c5425cfefab1206e21032ae90eac30febb018","tid":1502372,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:58:59.000Z","msg":"警方晚上10時半，在深水埗警署附近的欽州街，向示威者方向快速推進，示威者後退至鴨寮街等內街。現場警員其後在近晚上11時返回警署內。<br />\n<br />\n警員推進期間，有一名警員用警棍指向身穿記者反光背心的無綫電視女記者。幾名警員其後包圍該名記者，叫她不要動，又要求其他記者讓開。該名女記者及其他記者表明身份，質疑警方為何拘捕記者。該名女記者在警方傳媒聯絡隊檢查記者證後獲放行。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台<br />\n#香港警察<br />\n#無綫電視<br />\n#TVB<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/1085010011697420/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fvideos%2F1085010011697420%2F&d=BZKFieMwLRuYRu3HtqC84hVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=ae47b2d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/videos/1085010011697420/</a>"},{"pid":"c8f27c14141d7b96683ef26b5a85b0dde788b74c","tid":1502372,"uid":286964,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:59:32.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n(正經)(請給我長期置頂) 整合被控義士進程 一個也不能少不是口號！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1502159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1502159</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f2b107660d340593fec6a2e9d31fab7876a9686d","tid":1502372,"uid":135867,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T15:59:43.000Z","msg":"有無全段睇"},{"pid":"8317b22c4439d47a22d151a85ad6fd16b2387ee7","tid":1502372,"uid":107656,"like":234,"dislike":1,"score":233,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:00:22.000Z","msg":"黨營電視台都敢查<br />\n當黨死架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e9e1b638ed326ccba58b0bf172c13643de778cb","tid":1502372,"uid":146055,"like":114,"dislike":1,"score":113,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T16:01:31.000Z","msg":"肯定又唔報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/